title.rendered: 2 Chainz Live in Jakarta Presented by Prestige Motorcars

content.rendered:
He is a world famous rapper who goes by the name 2 Chainz. Celebrated by his hit songs, “I’m different”, “It’s a Vibe” and “Birthday Song”, the artist is synonymous with chart topping music alongside other world class musicians. This time, instead of Prestige Motorcars bringing in cars to Jakarta, we brought 2 Chainz. Held at Empirica, SCBD we gathered hip hop lovers from all around to experience 2 Chainz in live concert. Many people, many nice cars and most importantly many memories and good times to be shared.
